WEBVTT

00:03:28.343 --> 00:03:30.202
Drugi gospodin bi odvratio,

00:03:30.202 --> 00:03:31.493
(farsi: "Otvaram ti svoju košulju."),

00:03:31.493 --> 00:03:34.172
što znači "Otvaram ti svoju košulju."

00:03:34.724 --> 00:03:36.591
Prvi bi odvratio,

00:03:36.615 --> 00:03:37.710
(farsi: Tvoj sam sluga.),

00:03:37.710 --> 00:03:39.749
što znači: "Tvoj sam sluga."

00:03:39.773 --> 00:03:42.139
A drugi bi na to odvratio:

00:03:42.163 --> 00:03:44.230
(farsi: "Ja sam prašina
pod tvojim nogama."),

00:03:44.230 --> 00:03:46.904
doslovno: "Ja sam prašina
pod tvojim nogama."

00:03:46.904 --> 00:03:47.993
(Smijeh)

00:03:48.017 --> 00:03:50.999
Evo slike, ako niste shvatili.


00:03:50.999 --> 00:03:52.231
(Smijeh)

00:03:52.231 --> 00:03:54.744
Podijelio sam to s vama jer

00:03:54.768 --> 00:03:59.295
s novim jezicima dolaze
novi koncepti koji prije nisu postojali.

00:03:59.319 --> 00:04:00.477
A druga stvar je,